<br />PC == free speech. Consoles == only big companies can speak. From <a href="http://warioworld.com/apply/" class="postlink">console developer qualifications</a>: "Nintendo looks for companies that are established game developers [...] working from a secure business location [...] not located within a personal residence."

		

